{{az-variant|c=јардым|r=yardım|a=یاردیم}}

===Etymology===
According to most scholars, a derivation of {{der|az|fa|یار|tr=yâr}}<ref>{{R:trk:ESTJa|vol=IV|pages=142-143}}</ref>.
Alternatively, from a barely attested stem {{m|und|*yar-|}}, in which case possibly related to {{m|trk-cmn|*yara-||to be good enough}}. See {{cog|tr|yardım}} for Turkic cognates.

